The paper deals with the problem of phase retrieval, which is a common topic in information theory (cs.IT) and computer vision (cs.CV). The use of subspaces is also a common theme in machine learning (cs.LG) and numerical analysis (cs.NA). The algorithmic approach and theoretical guarantees may also fall under the category of signal processing (cs.SI).
